#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:2883
msgid "System default output"
msgstr "Standard-Systemausgabe"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:2910
msgid "All local outputs, in sync"
msgstr "Alle lokalen Ausgänge, synchron"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:2927
msgid "Plays on every connected speaker at the same time — wired outputs are delayed to stay in step with Bluetooth."
msgstr "Spielt gleichzeitig auf jedem verbundenen Lautsprecher — kabelgebundene Ausgänge werden verzögert, um mit Bluetooth im Takt zu bleiben."

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:2941
#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:2948
msgid "Sync fine-tune"
msgstr "Sync-Feinabstimmung"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:2958
msgid "If the Bluetooth speaker still trails the wired ones, raise this until they play together."
msgstr "Hinkt der Bluetooth-Lautsprecher den kabelgebundenen noch hinterher, erhöhe dies, bis sie zusammen spielen."

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:2970
msgid "Sync delay in milliseconds"
msgstr "Sync-Verzögerung in Millisekunden"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:2987
msgid "Type an exact delay in milliseconds — the slider moves in steps of ten."
msgstr "Geben Sie eine genaue Verzögerung in Millisekunden ein — der Regler bewegt sich in Zehnerschritten."

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:2991
msgid "ms"
msgstr "ms"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3005
msgid "Calibrate with the microphone"
msgstr "Mit dem Mikrofon kalibrieren"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3010
msgid "Plays a few loud clicks through each speaker and measures with the microphone how far the Bluetooth speaker trails — the delay is set automatically."
msgstr "Spielt ein paar laute Klicks durch jeden Lautsprecher und misst mit dem Mikrofon, wie weit der Bluetooth-Lautsprecher hinterherhinkt — die Verzögerung wird automatisch gesetzt."

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3030
msgid "Round 1 of 2 — clicks through every speaker…"
msgstr "Runde 1 von 2 — Klicks durch jeden Lautsprecher…"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3031
msgid "Round 2 of 2 — quiet, checking the result…"
msgstr "Runde 2 von 2 — still, Ergebnis wird geprüft…"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3061
msgid "%1 plays in the group"
msgstr "%1 spielt in der Gruppe"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3074
msgid "Whether this speaker plays in the group — untick to leave it out without disconnecting it. Remembered for the device."
msgstr "Ob dieser Lautsprecher in der Gruppe spielt — Haken entfernen, um ihn auszulassen, ohne die Verbindung zu trennen. Wird für das Gerät gemerkt."

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3080
msgid "%1 (nothing plugged in)"
msgstr "%1 (nichts angeschlossen)"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3090
msgid "Balance of %1"
msgstr "Balance von %1"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3099
msgid "This speaker's share of the volume — the balance follows every master move and is remembered for the device. It scales only what this widget plays; the per-device volume in the system's audio settings is a separate, untouched layer — which is why those numbers differ from these sliders."
msgstr "Der Anteil dieses Lautsprechers an der Lautstärke — die Balance folgt jeder Bewegung des Hauptreglers und wird für das Gerät gemerkt. Sie wirkt nur auf die Wiedergabe dieses Widgets; die gerätebezogene Lautstärke in den Systemeinstellungen ist eine eigene, unberührte Ebene — deshalb weichen deren Zahlen von diesen Reglern ab."

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3116
msgctxt "compact: speaker plays the left channel"
msgid "L"
msgstr "L"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3117
msgctxt "compact: speaker plays the right channel"
msgid "R"
msgstr "R"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3118
msgctxt "compact: speaker plays a mono mix"
msgid "M"
msgstr "M"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3119
msgctxt "compact: speaker plays plain stereo"
msgid "ST"
msgstr "ST"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3124
msgid "Which channels this speaker plays: stereo, left only, right only, or a mono mix of both. Set one speaker to L and another to R for a true stereo pair — remembered for the device."
msgstr "Welche Kanäle dieser Lautsprecher spielt: Stereo, nur links, nur rechts oder ein Mono-Mix aus beiden. Stellen Sie einen Lautsprecher auf L und einen anderen auf R für ein echtes Stereopaar — wird für das Gerät gemerkt."

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3154
msgid "Bluetooth"
msgstr "Bluetooth"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3169
msgid "Bluetooth is off or no adapter is available — check System Settings."
msgstr "Bluetooth ist ausgeschaltet oder kein Adapter verfügbar — prüfe die Systemeinstellungen."

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3180
msgid "No paired Bluetooth audio devices — pair the speaker once in System Settings and it appears here."
msgstr "Keine gekoppelten Bluetooth-Audiogeräte — kopple den Lautsprecher einmal in den Systemeinstellungen, dann erscheint er hier."

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3194
msgid "%1 — connecting…"
msgstr "%1 — Verbindung wird hergestellt …"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3212
msgid "%1 — pairing…"
msgstr "%1 — wird gekoppelt…"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3213
msgid "%1 — new, click to pair"
msgstr "%1 — neu, zum Koppeln klicken"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3224
msgid "Pair a new speaker…"
msgstr "Neuen Lautsprecher koppeln…"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3240
msgid "Searching — put the speaker in pairing mode…"
msgstr "Suche läuft — versetze den Lautsprecher in den Kopplungsmodus…"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3261
msgid "WiFi & network"
msgstr "WLAN & Netzwerk"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3293
msgid "%1 (speaker group)"
msgstr "%1 (Lautsprechergruppe)"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3321
msgid "Balance"
msgstr "Balance"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3335
msgid "This device's share of the volume — the balance follows every master move and is remembered for the device."
msgstr "Der Anteil dieses Geräts an der Lautstärke — die Balance folgt jeder Bewegung des Hauptreglers und wird für das Gerät gemerkt."

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3357
msgid "Each device buffers on its own, so rooms may play a few seconds apart. For perfectly synced speakers, group them in the Google Home app — the group appears here as a single device."
msgstr "Jedes Gerät puffert den Stream für sich, daher können Räume einige Sekunden versetzt spielen. Für perfekt synchrone Lautsprecher gruppieren Sie sie in der Google-Home-App — die Gruppe erscheint hier als ein einzelnes Gerät."

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3367
msgid "Stop casting everywhere"
msgstr "Wiedergabe auf allen Geräten stoppen"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3385
msgid "Searching for devices…"
msgstr "Suche nach Geräten…"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3394
msgid "No devices found on your network"
msgstr "Keine Geräte in Ihrem Netzwerk gefunden"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3416
msgid "Volume: %1% (scroll to adjust)"
msgstr "Lautstärke: %1 % (zum Ändern scrollen)"

